WEBVTT

00:03.503 --> 00:06.199
[Man] We're ahead of schedule.
[Man #2]
That's a first, huh?

00:07.273 --> 00:09.241
Wanna grab some coffee?

00:09.309 --> 00:12.938
No. I gotta get home.
We're meeting the wedding planner.

00:13.013 --> 00:14.947
I thought
that was last night.

00:15.015 --> 00:17.950
No, last night was the caterer.
Should have taken my advice.

00:18.018 --> 00:19.952
Should have just eloped.

00:20.020 --> 00:22.750
Well, it's too late now.
No, it's not, man.
You can do it.

00:22.822 --> 00:26.758
Hop on a plane tonight.
Go to Vegas.
Boom. It's all over.

00:26.826 --> 00:30.887
Rachel's mom
would never speak to me again.

00:30.964 --> 00:32.898
That's the best argument
to do it.

00:32.966 --> 00:35.560
I been trying to get
my mother-in-law to shut up
for five years.

00:35.635 --> 00:38.365
- Whoa, what's this?
- What the hell are they doing?

00:43.443 --> 00:44.967
Hit the brakes!
I'm trying!

00:45.045 --> 00:47.275
Try the emergency brake!
This is Baker Four.

00:47.347 --> 00:49.815
We're on Vinton and Hillside.
It's a hijacking.

00:49.883 --> 00:51.874
I repeat,
we are being hijacked.

00:51.951 --> 00:54.283
- <i>[Radio Crackling]</i>
- They're jammin' us.

00:57.123 --> 00:58.715
[Radio Crackling]

